tag_list: news, make-money, policy, business, sports, entertainment, bangladesh, citizen-journalism
overview:
OutLookBD.com is a dynamic news portal where you will find latest news of round the globe. Its the First initiative from Bangladesh on Citizen Journalism, means any one can send and publish report/news/article/feature of any event and issues happening in front of them. Citizen Journalism is quite a new concept in the world of journalism. It Helps to find unbiased reports and get the actual insight of the news.

Any body can make money, working from there home. It also gives the opportunity to mass to interact with a greater audience and a platform to easily make attention of any thing that anybody think interesting and/or important. Its a UGC based digital media
